At Ramada Beach Hotel, Ajman, gracious hospitality is a philosophy we extend throughout every level of our organization. Providing opportunities for personal and professional development, Ramada Beach Hotel invites you to be a part of their professional team\\\!
Desired Candidate Profile
We are currently looking for :-
Assistant FB Manager
The right candidate should have the following:-
•	Similar experience in international hotels preferably in UAE/Gulf.
•	Strong leadership ability and ability to create, maintain & motivate a Team
•	Good English communication skills and Excellent Guest Relation Skills
